data.text: @Tinn7Jacqueline Awww that’s good you are feeling well. I can understand your worry, here’s hoping they will be fine. How exciting having twins on  the way 😊😊

@Tig_gordon Thank you. I felt terrible all day yesterday and I had 2 negative tests, actually feel a lot better today and result was positive. Yes she is my main worry, as long as her and babies are ok 🤗

@jo92188950 Thank you Jo, I'm fully vaccinated and don't feel too bad. She has had no vaccinations and I was so worried for her and the babies, just glad she is feeling a lot better today. Have a lovely Friday Jo 😀🤗
@Tinn7Jacqueline I’m pleased for her but not for you. I hope you feel ok 🤗
@mikesaltsman194 Thank you Mike she is feeling a whole lot better this morning 👍
@Tig_gordon Thank you she is feeling a lot better today and I tested positive this morning 🙄

@Tinn7Jacqueline Oh no sorry to see you have it now too. Glad you’re not feeling too poorly. Glad your daughter is feeling better. Not what either if you needed right now. Sending hugs and hope that your daughter keeps improving and that you stay well too 🤗🤗🤗🤗

@Tinn7Jacqueline I'm so glad your daughter feels better, she has enough to contend with bless her x
Hopefully you won't feel too bad lovely xx
